title Authentication Sequence spa app

browser->server: HTTP GET https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/spa
server->browser: text-html
browser->server: HTTP GET https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/main.css
server-->browser: main.css
browser->server: HTTP GET https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/main.js
server-->browser: main.js

browser->server: HTTP GET https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/data.json
server-->browser: [{ content: "HTML is easy", date: "2019-05-23" }, ...]

note over browser:
browser executes the event handler that render notes to display,
included the new added
end note

browser->server: HTTP POST https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note_spa
server->browser: application/json

note over browser:
Send data asyncronously the form, with the new_note_spa method
preventing the form from refreshing the page.
end note

note over server:
Server modifies the json object adding the new note,
sending back the new json object with the new note
end note